<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA13d196hn7-ptr" id="PJA13d196hn7">hn7</a>

   <p>(5) establishing</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA13d196hn8-ptr" id="PJA13d196hn8">hn8</a>

